RNAseq Analysis

2024-04-09

Quality Control

Sequencing quality control was performed using FastQC and trimmomatic. No major issues were observed. Some samples displayed adapter contamination which was removed during read trimming. Alignment rates for all samples were above >80% indicating no major problems. No samples will be excluded from the downstream analysis
